ComicInfo.Title: Seshat
ComicInfo.Summary: In desperate need for money, Conrad tries to fool the mysterious Dr. Branko but is not successful. And he still cannot forget his magic journeys into lust and ecstasy, meeting the old Egyptian goddesses one by one. He succumbs again and chooses Seschat, the fifth daughter of Isis. Her specialty: she can change into characters every man would like to have sex with. Conrad's pop-culture-fed mind goes into overdrive! More great, lusciously drawn, supernatural sex from Germany, from the producers of the Eros hit Alraune!
